heading.emphasis:
List of
Coenosia
species known from Siberia

subSubSection.paragraph: In view of the vast size of Siberia, its ecological diversity and the paucity of the faunistic literature, some additional faunistic data on previously described species are included in this list, based on material studied and newly identified in ZMUM and SZNM . In the lists of specimens given below, “( ZMUM )” identifies material examined from that collection, whilst all other material is in SZNM .
